'''Update''' is a special form of <code>!</code> in K4/qdb<ref>https://code.kx.com/q/basics/funsql/#update</ref> which takes 4 arguments. It updates a given table with the help of the given arguments.

* <code>x</code> is the table to be modified.
* <code>y</code> specifies the conditions to select rows.
* <code>z</code>, a dict, selects columns and gives the placeholder names to use in <code>u</code>.
* <code>u</code>, a dict, specifies what should be done to the selected cells.

